en hill", "united states", "fitzgerald"], "number": ["2024271014", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2024271015", "2024271012", "2024271013", "1350104569", "online resource", "2995-9799"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the leader enterprise and press (fitzgerald, ben hill county, georgia) 1915-1921 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 74.021194, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["ben hill county (ga.)", "georgia", "ben hill county", "ben hill", "united states", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "fitzgerald", "newspapers", "journaux"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The leader enterprise and press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271013/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271014/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1921", "dates": ["[1921 TO 1964]"], "description": ["Weekly, January 12, 1922-September 10, 1964 Began with vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921); ceased with v. 69, no. 37 (Sept. 10, 1964). \"Official organ of the city of Fitzgerald.\"--vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921), page [4]. Publisher: Fitzgerald Leader Company, Inc., April 4, 1963-September 10, 1964. For some issues in April 1921, stated frequency is \"published daily, tri-weekly.\" Cannot be detemined whether the two frequencies constitute separate editions; they seem more likely to be the same title available in different subscriptions. <March 9-April 1, 1921>, this title may have appeared also as part of Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : Daily), constituting the issue for certain days of the week. Merged with: Fitzgerald herald, to form: Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader. Vol. XXVI, No. 29 (March 9, 1921); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XXXVIII, No. 21 (May 26, 1927) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). 